ls0 ws0">God appointed labor as a blessing to man, </div><div class="t ma1e xbc he y2451 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to occupy his mind, to strengthen his body, </div><div class="t m616 xbc he y2413 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and to develop his faculties. In mental and </div><div class="t m9b4 xbc he y2195 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">physical activity, Adam found one of the </div><div class="t m107d x6e he y2209 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">highest pleasures of his holy existence.&quot;—</div><div class="t mefc xbc h21 y1f65 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Patriarchs and Prophets, </div><div class="t m371 xcd he y1f65 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 50. </div><div class="t m7cb x86 he y158f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m1222 xa5 he y1ff8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To sustain their physical needs, </div><div class="t m1fd3 x6e he y184f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what ideal diet was provided for </div><div class="t m54b x6e he y1a28 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Adam and Eve? Gen. 1:29; 2:16. </div><div class="t m13d xae he y214f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—&quot;In order to know what are the </div><div class="t md4 x6e he y1b8f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">best foods, we must study God&apos;s, original </div><div class="t m615 x6e he y1ee2 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">plan for man&apos;s diet. He who created man </div><div class="t m45c x6e he y1b24 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and who understands his needs appointed </div><div class="t m89 x6e he y1112 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Adam his food. &apos;Behold,&apos; He said, &apos;I have </div><div class="t m707 x6e he y1d22 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">given you every herb yielding seed, . . . </div><div class="t m2c6 xbc he y1ed0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and every tree, in which is the fruit of a </div><div class="t m727 x6e he y1c00 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tree yielding seed; to you it shall be for </div><div class="t mad7 x6e he y1fc7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">food.&apos; . . . </div><div class="t mb9d xbc he y1a04 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">